reviews.text: Delicious fresh sushi served in a gorgeous and authentic setting. Service was prompt and quick, wasn’t perfect but good. I was happy with my meal.
Always great food, service and fun!
Casual and relaxed cafe style eatery, average food but fast.
I ate intestines and it was nice.

Frankly, the food is excellent value and could cost 50% more and still be satisfied. Jennifer's answer below must have been a one-off, or she was expecting much more. The Omekase for lunch is only $480pp so perhaps she went for dinner and was disappointed. I shall return regularly as it is the best sushi place (for food in the area). Service is brusque, but quick and mostly reliable.

reviews.text:
The set lunch menu is quite value for money.  Fresh ingredients. If you want to order its special lunch menu, make sure to call and pre-order in advance. Efficient and friendly service.

For my second visit on 15 Mar 2019, its service was not as good as my first visit. Portion was also small.
A bit expensive for lunch ranging from 150 to 250hkd. The food is in good quality. But the seat and table is too crowded.
Great staff with excellent service, food is also good with variety of choices. Recommended.
Ok place when not busy
Sushi good good good👍👍👍
